## Learning Objectives

By the end of this module, you will be able to:

* Understand the basics of logical reasoning in computing
* Implement simple Boolean logic using physical materials
* Explain how machines can learn from trial and error
* Build and use decision trees for classification
* Describe the fundamentals of how machines learn patterns from data
* Recognize AI and ML concepts in everyday technology
